'''feh''' is [[Article description::an open-source image viewer that is most aimed at command-line users.]] It can be used to view images on disk or, more often, for setting the desktop background for tiling [[window managers]] like [[i3]]. It has several command line options to change the behaviour for either of these uses, mostly entered around how to resize the image for the view.

