==Usage==
To use it to set one's desktop background to a scaled version of a wallpaper:

<pre>
feh --bg-scale /path/to/WALLPAPER.jpg
</pre>

where <code>/path/to/WALLPAPER.jpg</code> is the path to the wallpaper one wishes to use as desktop background. Likewise to set the desktop background to a tiled version of the wallpaper:

<pre>
feh --bg-tile /path/to/WALLPAPER.jpg
</pre>

